---
---

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-overlay"></div>
  <div class="container cta-content">
    <span class="badge badge-gold">OFERTA LIMITADA</span>
    <h2 class="cta-title">TU PRIMERA SEMANA<br/><span class="text-red">ES GRATIS</span></h2>
    <p class="cta-sub">Sin compromiso. Sin tarjeta de credito. Solo tu y las pesas.</p>

    <div class="urgency-boxes">
      <div class="urgency-box">
        <span class="urgency-number">12</span>
        <span class="urgency-label">Cupos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="urgency-box">
        <span class="urgency-number">3</span>
        <span class="urgency-label">Dias</span>
      </div>
      <div class="urgency-box">
        <span class="urgency-number">7</span>
        <span class="urgency-label">Horas</span>
      </div>
      <div class="urgency-box">
        <span class="urgency-number">42</span>
        <span class="urgency-label">Min</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary cta-btn">RECLAMA TU SEMANA GRATIS</a>
    <p class="cta-fine">*Oferta valida para nuevos miembros. Sujeto a disponibilidad.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517836357463-d25dfeac3438?w=1920&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cta-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,10,10,0.93), rgba(220,38,38,0.4));
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .cta-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .urgency-boxes {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .urgency-box {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
    border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 10px) 0, 100% 10px, 100% 100%, 10px 100%, 0 calc(100% - 10px));
  }

  .urgency-number {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .urgency-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    padding: 1rem 3rem;
  }

  .cta-fine {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .urgency-boxes { gap: 0.5rem; }
    .urgency-box { width: 65px; height: 65px; }
    .urgency-number { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
